Info.Title: Diary of a Wimpy Kid
Info.Writer: Jackie Filgo (screenplay), Jeff Filgo (screenplay), Gabe Sachs (screenplay), Jeff Judah (screenplay), Jeff Kinney (book)
Info.Actors: Zachary Gordon, Robert Capron, Rachael Harris, Steve Zahn
Info.Plot: The adventures of a 12 year old who is fresh out of elementary and transitions to middle school, where he has to learn the consequences and responsibility to survive the year.
